g of the said Tuition and the grade of the Student and the Subject in advance. You are restrained from directly negotiate with the Tutor with regard to the fees/money for the said assignment. You should not approach the tutor to make personal visits without assigning the duty by the Swami Vivekananda Jnana Kendra and also you should not make payment to the Tutor directly. In such cases, Swami Vivekananda Jnana Kendra is at liberty to claim damages from you. Swami Vivekananda Jnana Kendra is not liable for any theft of belongings/money/jewelries etc., or robbery by the Tutor during the course of assignment. On such cases you are at liberty to approach the jurisdiction Police seeking relief as per law. Swami Vivekananda Jnana Kendra will not hold any responsibility for the physical mishandling or any harassment including Sexual Harassment etc., during assignment or any other time by the Tutor. On such cases you are at liberty to approach the jurisdiction Police seeking relief as per law. You have to behave with the Tutor as a prudent person. You should not physically mishandle or do any harassment including Sexual Harassment etc., at the time of assignment, during assignment or any other time to the Tutor. In such cases, necessary legal actions will be initiated as per Law. The Swami Vivekananda Jnana Kendra is at liberty to Cancel the assignment and modify the assignment and timings without prior notice to you. And further the Swami Vivekananda Jnana Kendra will inform you about any changes in the assignment and timings. In the case of change of the Tutor, you will be again provided with a Demo class to choose your Tutor. Swami Vivekananda Jnana Kendra is at liberty to change/modify/cancel your assignment forthwith on account of misconduct, including but not limited to, fraudulent, dishonest or undisciplined conduct, or breach of integrity, or embezzlement, or misappropriation or misuse or causing damage to the Company’s or Client’s property or breach of the confiden